Dmg 33, Dly 36. +2 vsMg +2 vsFire +2 vsCold +65 HP +5.00 Wt  <br>
<br>
It has a recommended level of 51; I'm not sure if that means you cannot equip it prior to that, or has reduced stats.<br>
